overview: DSK produced three surprising publicity videos carried by the very personal e-store platform Codeco.org for three highly peculiar products: Bin2pdf software, the antivirus Codeco aT, and Codeco T-shirts.  Bin2pdf ad (analogue backup).  2008, 1 min.  Codeco aT ad (analogue backup).  2008, 1 min.  Codeco T-shirt ad.  2008, 1 min.
